Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.46,0:00:06.30,Name,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(484,0)\pos(357,385)}D{\fnMeiryo U}ü{\fnNarkisim}sseldorf Federation • Holding Cells
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.27,0:00:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(357,468)}Please ask Helene and Custav for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.36,0:00:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ask them to record "Detective Forster."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.57,0:00:11.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.45,0:00:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They show reruns Tuesday mornings at ten.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.95,0:00:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've never seen it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.29,0:00:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a great show!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.33,0:00:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen here, Milch.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.62,0:00:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is no laughing matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.83,0:00:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know how much trouble you caused the boss...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.80,0:00:28.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because you messed up and got caught?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.30,0:00:31.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even for an idiot like you...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.30,0:00:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he was kind enough to send someone\Nlike myself as your attorney.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.55,0:00:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So show him some appreciation.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.76,0:00:41.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He only sent you to keep an eye on me, to\Nmake sure I didn't spill anything, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.02,0:00:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's correct.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.61,0:00:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Milch.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.32,0:00:48.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You do know what would happen\Nif you told the truth, don't you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.20,0:00:53.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.07,0:00:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't sell out my people.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.20,0:00:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.78,0:01:00.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just follow my scenario and confess, got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.25,0:01:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.46,0:01:04.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you already have the schedule\Nfor my next job figured out.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.96,0:01:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The next one...?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.59,0:01:09.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When do you think that will be?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.34,0:01:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.42,0:01:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who should think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.64,0:01:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who do you think I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.97,0:01:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Gunther Milch, the Escape King.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.06,0:01:24.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have time to waste on this nonsense.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.48,0:01:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.44,0:01:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you confess like I told you, you'll\Nget out in about five years.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.32,0:01:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you tell them for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.99,0:01:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.20,0:01:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell Helene and Custav to record\N"Detective Forster" for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.20,0:01:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but they're not really reliable...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.41,0:01:47.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I should try that again while I'm still at this station.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.29,0:01:49.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.45,0:03:27.45,Title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(400,0)\pos(362,361)}Decision
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.10,0:03:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure he's not faking it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.27,0:03:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.02,0:03:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there was blood in his vomit...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.40,0:03:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and his body feels so cold so...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.69,0:03:39.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't throw up here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.19,0:03:39.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.36,0:03:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're just in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.74,0:03:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep an eye on this place for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.83,0:03:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just now, some new kids they brought\Nin went nuts on the third floor...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.37,0:03:51.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I heard that some people were injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.67,0:03:54.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But this one looks like he's about to die...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.38,0:03:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You again, Milch?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.17,0:03:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just put him on the bed in the back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.46,0:03:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take a look at him later.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.38,0:04:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-Take me to a hospital!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.76,0:04:08.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be right back, so just wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.85,0:04:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, they keep bringing them in one after another today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.82,0:04:23.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.57,0:04:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to be next to a serial killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.03,0:04:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Why does it have to be here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.12,0:04:29.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop complaining!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.75,0:04:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got him on an I.V. drip because he\Ncollapsed after not eating anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.13,0:04:38.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel worse lying next to a guy like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.21,0:04:40.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just shut up and lie down!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.63,0:04:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doctor, you said people were injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.05,0:04:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know how many?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.68,0:04:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.59,0:04:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't know unless I go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.26,0:04:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.35,0:04:50.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make those kids pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.27,0:04:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About what you said the other day...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.90,0:05:01.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.78,0:05:07.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.96,0:05:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm thinking of killing someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.92,0:05:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your former fiancee...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.63,0:05:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eva Heinemann.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.22,0:05:27.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.47,0:05:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think that's a great idea?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.76,0:05:34.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, she knows too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.94,0:05:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On that rainy day at the building under construction...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.81,0:05:40.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she heard three gunshots...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.15,0:05:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.15,0:05:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saw him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.57,0:05:49.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't need people like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.95,0:05:51.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't, do we?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.70,0:05:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.20,0:05:55.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.37,0:05:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.83,0:05:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.21,0:06:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eva would never testify about thatI
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.96,0:06:04.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She only wants me to be imprisoned for life!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.88,0:06:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All she thinks about is making\\Nme regret leaving her forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.55,0:06:12.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She'll only testify to things that'll hurt me
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.89,0:06:14.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.10,0:06:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So.. !
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.14,0:06:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I asked if it was a great idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.11,0:06:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she were to disappear...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.02,0:06:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you might not be sent to prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.36,0:06:35.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her death would he beneficial to both of us you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.87,0:06:40.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you tell the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.08,0:06:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will they believe a story like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.92,0:06:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you tell your attorney, Mr. Verdeman?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.68,0:06:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He might be one of my allies, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.23,0:07:00.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll make sure you're found innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.06,0:07:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"We" being the excellent lawyers, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.07,0:07:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once you're free and you step outside...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.44,0:07:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you'll he able to have a nice drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.45,0:07:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, by then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.20,0:07:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that spoiled, loud-mouthed, drunken bitch...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.91,0:07:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will be gone from this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.34,0:07:32.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.65,0:07:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to be kidding me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.31,0:07:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stuck next to a murderer like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.02,0:07:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Milch!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.23,0:07:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep your mouth shut!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.36,0:07:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you just stay silent to your heart's content!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.99,0:07:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Milch!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.95,0:07:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just going to confess and get transferred\Nto prison in the next five days!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.83,0:08:00.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then it'll be goodbye to murderers like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.12,0:08:02.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you shouting about?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.62,0:08:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Milch!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.54,0:08:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty energetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.29,0:08:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.04,0:08:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you were faking it after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.92,0:08:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that felt good!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.05,0:08:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just have to endure for five more days!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.05,0:08:14.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I won't be associated with killers like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.22,0:08:16.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enough already
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.31,0:08:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.74,0:08:32.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in five days, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.82,0:08:38.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, on that rainy night...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.12,0:08:41.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you heard three gunshots in a building\Nthat was under construction...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.12,0:08:46.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and saw a young, blonde man coming down the stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.84,0:08:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.05,0:08:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.97,0:08:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.93,0:08:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you still plan on tackling this case\Nwhile denying Johan's existence?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.80,0:08:59.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.72,0:09:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Eva Heinemann.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.89,0:09:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May I have you present this important testimony in court?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.87,0:09:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.73,0:09:31.23,Name,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(250,200)\pos(353,389)}D{\fnMeiryo U}ü{\fnNarkisim}sseldorf Federal Police Station
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.29,0:09:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(358,467)}What does Dr. Tenma want this late at night?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.92,0:09:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does he mean, he has something\Nimportant he wants to tell us?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.51,0:09:35.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.51,0:09:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he just asked to see the investigators.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.94,0:09:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you want to talk about, Dr. Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.74,0:09:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In D{\fnMeiryo U}ü{\fnNarkisim}sseldorf... Eisler Memorial Hospital...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.16,0:09:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Director Heinemann...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.49,0:10:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surgical Director Oppenheim...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.21,0:10:06.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Boyer...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.79,0:10:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and my patient, Adolf Junkers...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.76,0:10:22.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.26,0:10:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.15,0:10:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.03,0:10:35.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,killed them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.17,0:10:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A gust of wind came...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.42,0:10:51.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The thermos fell over...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.15,0:10:54.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sandwiches were all dirty...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.05,0:11:00.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the time, he...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.31,0:11:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,just sadly smiled...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.92,0:11:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}According to an announcement made by the police...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.17,0:11:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}early on the morning of the fourth...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.67,0:11:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the suspectf Kenzou Tenma, who had consistently\Ndenied involvement in a string of murders...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.60,0:11:26.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}completely reversed his position and confessed to\Nthe murders of Eisler Memorial Hospital's director...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.52,0:11:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and two physicians in D{\fnMeiryo U}ü{\fnNarkisim}sseldorf...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.94,0:11:32.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}as well as the murder of Adolf Junkers.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.48,0:11:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He has made a full confession.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.78,0:11:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.16,0:11:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This just in.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.99,0:11:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He confessed? That's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.53,0:11:43.95,Default 2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}According to an announcement made by the police...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.54,0:11:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}early on the morning of the fourth...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.04,0:11:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the suspect, Kenzou Tenma, who had consistently\Ndenied involvement in a string of murder cases...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.46,0:11:54.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}has confessed to all of the charges against him.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.05,0:11:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mess with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.63,0:12:02.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell did you guys do to Dr. Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.89,0:12:07.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of torture did you put him through\Nto squeeze that false confession out of him?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.89,0:12:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could you please let go?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.31,0:12:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.48,0:12:13.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just let me see Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.90,0:12:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to talk to him myself and have him tell me what\Nkind of treatment he received during his questioning!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.32,0:12:20.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's useless, Dr. Reichwein.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.49,0:12:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He even refused an interview with\Nme, and I'm his attorney.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.71,0:12:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would seem that his confession was indeed voluntary.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.79,0:12:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.59,0:12:39.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've looked into it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.76,0:12:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know the investigator myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.72,0:12:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not a man who's capable of torture.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.51,0:12:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems Tenma simply confessed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.77,0:12:51.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It went surprisingly smoothly, I heard...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.02,0:12:53.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Verdeman!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.35,0:12:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me you also believe his confession is real!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.28,0:13:03.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't tell what his intent is unless I interview him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.28,0:13:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe in him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.70,0:13:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dr. Tenma is innocent!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.21,0:13:16.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe in him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.60,0:13:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Verdeman speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.68,0:13:33.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Mr. Baul.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.60,0:13:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm terribly sorry for not being there at a time\Nlike this, but I had to attend to an emergency.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.73,0:13:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.15,0:13:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So, how was it?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.49,0:13:42.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Did Dr. Tenma...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.11,0:13:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, he refused my interview.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.95,0:13:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.82,0:13:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as we were trying really hard to prove his innocence...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.58,0:13:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and have them drop the false charges...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.58,0:13:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he makes a full confession.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.17,0:14:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Your father, on the other hand,\Nwas quite an admirable person.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.21,0:14:03.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how grueling the interrogation...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.72,0:14:05.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he never faltered one step...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.89,0:14:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and continued to plead his innocence.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.31,0:14:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}His innocence...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.10,0:14:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.85,0:14:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,what shall we do, Mr. Verdeman?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.82,0:14:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mr. Verdeman?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.65,0:14:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That woman...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.32,0:14:27.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What was her name again?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.16,0:14:31.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That important witness who can prove Tenma's innocence.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.45,0:14:33.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Eva Heinemann.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.29,0:14:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Where is she right now?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.38,0:14:39.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At a hotel in the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.42,0:14:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would certainly like to meet her in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.76,0:14:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.80,0:14:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a difficult woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.39,0:14:49.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For now, I'll try meeting with her myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.81,0:14:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My father was admirable?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.88,0:15:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please open the door, Miss Eva Heinemann.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.17,0:15:24.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you're in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.72,0:15:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The maids complained that they couldn't make the bed...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.63,0:15:32.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because you were in here drinking all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.72,0:15:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Heinemann.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.64,0:15:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I fully understand that you hate Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.64,0:15:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If your relationship with Dr. Tenma had continued\Neven after you lost your father, the Director...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.36,0:15:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,your life would have been nice and easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.32,0:15:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Dr. Tenma left you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.28,0:15:56.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that Dr. Tenma ruined your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.16,0:15:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My father...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.71,0:16:03.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My father was... imprisoned as a suspected spy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.63,0:16:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For the longest time...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.38,0:16:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was shunned, as the son of a spy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.47,0:16:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I also had my life ruined by my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.64,0:16:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I didn't give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.06,0:16:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you think that is?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.23,0:16:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you think I was able to keep fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.40,0:16:24.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I believed in him...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.57,0:16:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My father was innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.57,0:16:29.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My father was innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.24,0:16:33.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My father was innocent!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.12,0:16:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.28,0:16:37.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Innocent!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.79,0:16:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The people I believe in must be innocent!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.67,0:16:44.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's get Tenma's false charges dismissed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.17,0:16:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenma has to be innocent!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.55,0:16:47.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like my father...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.63,0:16:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My father had to have been innocent!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.64,0:17:02.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My partner's and my contact information is written here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.27,0:17:06.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please give us a call when you're ready to testify.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.88,0:17:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.05,0:17:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're sending him to prison tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.22,0:17:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's only been a few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.97,0:17:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Apparently, it's because Tenma's\Nconfession went so smoothly.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.27,0:17:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't we do anything, Mr. Verdeman?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.93,0:17:47.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The police are also trying to convince\NTenma to meet with us, but...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.07,0:17:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}By the way, how is Miss Eva Heinemann?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.44,0:17:51.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She went out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.90,0:17:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's probably getting drunk at some bar again.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.62,0:18:03.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D{\fnMeiryo U}ü{\fnNarkisim}sseldorf.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.04,0:18:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything looks so familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.34,0:18:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate this town!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.79,0:18:42.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you're here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.08,0:18:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been sitting here for five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.25,0:18:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.33,0:18:50.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a really interesting paper, so I was copying it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.55,0:18:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,D-Do you want to go somewhere else?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.22,0:18:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.59,0:18:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go out for lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.26,0:18:58.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where do you want to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.64,0:18:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Italian?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.72,0:19:01.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or how about French?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.35,0:19:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you keep writing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.81,0:19:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you stay there and keep writing?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.77,0:19:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eva!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.06,0:19:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eva!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.17,0:19:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.26,0:19:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I'm so, glad for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.88,0:19:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See? Isn't it delicious?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.34,0:19:39.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.64,0:19:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.31,0:19:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.89,0:19:50.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we put rocks down like this, the blanket\Nwon't blow away in the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.36,0:19:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't talking,about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.90,0:19:54.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm asking why you're spreading it out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.44,0:19:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nice having lunch in a place like this once in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.78,0:19:59.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The weather's nice, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.78,0:20:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lunch? Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.91,0:20:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Us, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.41,0:20:06.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I made some sandwiches.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.29,0:20:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope you like them.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.58,0:20:09.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are bugs.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.04,0:20:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.29,0:20:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is so stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.47,0:20:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're all dirty now...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.10,0:20:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're ruined.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.45,0:20:43.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want one too, lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.08,0:20:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Franz!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.25,0:20:48.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's rude!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.79,0:20:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.22,0:21:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it good?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.89,0:21:11.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Start walking.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.78,0:21:26.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.67,0:21:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.80,0:21:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't get through to Mr. Verdeman.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.55,0:21:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm calling you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.80,0:21:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, his wife just gave birth, so he's probably\Nstill at the maternity center.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.81,0:21:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've heard about you, Miss Eva Heinemann.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.44,0:21:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please, feel free to tell me anything you'd like.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.11,0:21:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.86,0:22:00.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}About what?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.82,0:22:03.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The testimony to prove Tenma's innocence.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.65,0:22:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I see. We're very grateful!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.95,0:22:08.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.12,0:22:09.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}what hotel are you staying at right now?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.59,0:22:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Got it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.84,0:22:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll head over there right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.78,0:22:30.95,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(170,472)}Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.95,0:22:44.38,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(199,475)}Cherish what you know is true in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.95,0:22:44.38,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(201,21)}Ima kono sekai de wakaru koto mitsumete
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.38,0:22:47.34,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(182,472)}Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.34,0:23:01.02,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(198,472)}Please believe in the kindness of your eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.34,0:23:01.02,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(199,21)}Anata no hitomi no yasashisa wo shinjite
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.62,0:23:25.88,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(196,473)}Make it home to your land of harmony
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.88,0:23:34.30,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(195,473)}Make it home to your land of purity
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.30,0:23:36.76,Karaoke,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,246)\pos(187,472)}Make it home
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.89,0:22:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
